#: ../../docs/classes/class_texturebutton.rst:94
msgid ""
"If ``true``, the texture stretches to the edges of the node's bounding "
"rectangle using the :ref:`stretch_mode "
"<class_TextureButton_property_stretch_mode>`. If ``false``, the texture "
"will not scale with the node."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``true``，则使用 :ref:`stretch_mode "
"<class_TextureButton_property_stretch_mode>`，将纹理拉伸到节点边界矩形的边缘。如果为 "
"``false``，则纹理将不会随节点缩放。"

