#: ../../docs/classes/class_texturebutton.rst:110
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Controls the texture's behavior when you resize the node's bounding "
"rectangle, **only if** :ref:`expand "
"<class_TextureButton_property_expand>` is ``true``. Set it to one of the "
":ref:`StretchMode <enum_TextureButton_StretchMode>` constants. See the "
"constants to learn more."
msgstr ""
"调整节点的边界矩形大小时，控制纹理的行为，**仅当**:ref:`expand "
"<class_TextureButton_property_expand>` 为 ``true``。将其设置为 ``STRETCH_*`` "
"常量之一。参见常量以了解更多信息。"

